Properties.Caption: Просмотр справочника по ППС
Properties.Tag: Select [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_ITEM].[CITEM] As [Показатель ПС], [K_ITEM_1].[CITEM] As [Категория работников ГУ], Sum([FOT_SPR].[SUMM]) As [1 год (Отношение)], Sum([FOT_SPR].[SUMM_1]) As [2 год (Отношение)], Sum([FOT_SPR].[SUMM_2]) As [3 год (Отношение)], Sum([FOT_SPR].[SUMM_3]) As [4 год (Отношение)] From (((([FOT_SPR] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([FOT_SPR].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_ITEM] With (NoLock) On ([FOT_SPR].[K_ITEMID]=[K_ITEM].[K_ITEMID])) Inner Join [K_ITEM] As [K_ITEM_1] With (NoLock) On ([FOT_SPR].[K_ITEMID_1]=[K_ITEM_1].[K_ITEMID])) Where [DOC].[K_TDID]=1909 And |0 Group by [DOC].[CDOC], [K_ITEM].[CITEM], [K_ITEM_1].[CITEM] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр справочника по ППС
